{"type": "article", "id": 22040, "title": "我们觉得春节你会这样过，被戳中了吗？", "description": "难道你以前不是这样过的？那我羡慕你。", "date": "2016-02-08T08:00:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6945, "name": "春节"}, {"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}], "category": 3, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 115, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607134737iDS9IRq0OcB7CVg5.gif", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\"><b>1. 这是一年中进食最多的一周。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726151100ghFRqtPwUQ0rpcY3.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63243243\" data-format=\"gif\"></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2. 告别外卖 app 的一周。<span style=\"text-align: center;\"> </span></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134717KY1taiXoM6cUeB98.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3. （应该）也是工作量最少的一周。  <br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134719Nt7JosI0Q9vWgS3k.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.448\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4. 和爸爸妈妈在一起。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071347198KtDpm4CrHWOBzGI.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48953488\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5. 见了好久没见的老朋友。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713472020UE9bI7O1isBgx5.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.512\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>6. 以及老朋友的对象/娃。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134721thXKZGe2b4oAJQ0s.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75250836\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><span style=\"text-align: left;\"><b>7. 总的来说能放假都是高兴的。  </b></span></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134722E6TLbsRZABO2YJG3.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>8. 免不了也有感觉崩溃的时刻。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134722XE1cK3gLZYqDTmUC.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>9. 例如又回答了很多关于人生的大问题。 <br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134723Vf21BtEHsK7NvGwI.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>10. 不光是七大姑八大姨。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134724Eo274w80vYJZsNbK.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>11. 忍不住自己都开始思考人生……</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134724c5ZIGdYjX9gWHM8k.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>12. 想到一半意识到过几天又要上班/吃外卖。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134725cxKIgUPlNJveyQMR.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>13. 想啥想，吃吧。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134725HbcpXORmzCvjtB2M.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>14. 还有很多时间用来补剧/片。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134726WZM0KFipoySD41Em.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>15. 也想过好好看书，对了《好奇心日报》做过好多年度总结呢！<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/cards/20065.html\">点这里看看。</a></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134726t8SM0ODrwkpRC9f5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.396875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>16. 总结看的有点累……</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134727pwa3dGszk02EoSKv.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>17. 嗯，再看个动画片休息下吧！</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071347299rCWLFZEHx3Pthwl.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>18. 从北方回南方的同学，再次被提醒，没有暖气的家乡更冷。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134729eL5FGXzQrlf21w9i.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>19. 从南方回北方的同学，皮肤好干。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134730mTkYIabF5dfhnv2r.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72727273\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>20. 还有那些去旅游度假的同学，拍了多少照片？</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134732NegQB9bE8IHc740T.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.826\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>21. 最满意的自拍永远是下一张。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134732PSpF7jLatvK5zEun.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>22. </b><b>一年又一年，</b><b>我们最需要和平共处的对象是自己的脸。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134732JIFXVfHA7t9OP8bc.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56327543\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>23.  又度过了人生的七天。 暂时不想上称。  </b></span></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134733V2XMz3WND9CdF4li.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>24. 可能你觉得上述收获太无聊了。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134734SvGYZtoEsVUJXq68.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83409091\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>25. 不然你要怎样？</b></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071347355HFUK6lhkdBL4apR.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b><br></b></p>\n<p><b>26. 如果你有什么特别的，快点告诉我们吧。</b></p>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134735nefgZrVYJijB4GUK.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.92307692\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>27. </b><b>P.S. 没有可以编。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071347367wgHKNC3saykneQd.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<p class=\"\">动图来自<a href=\"http://giphy.com/gifs/thisisjason-art-loop-jason-clarke-tQ4yv6dxnDBNS\"> giphy.com</a></p>\n\n\n\n\n"}